apiVersion: v2
name: ppl-prun-utils
description: A Helm chart for the ppl-prun-utils Python scheduler service on HCC K8s
type: application

# Chart version — bump this every time you change anything inside helm/
# Follows SemVer (https://semver.org/)
version: 0.1.0

# App version — should track the application's version (pyproject.toml)
appVersion: "0.1.0"
















